"menuchoice> विकल्पः । संवादपेटिका दृश्यते ।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s Add Address Book dialog</"
"screeninfo>"
