"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s Add Address Book dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kaddressbook;'s Add Address Book संवाद</phrase> इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s Add Address Book dialog. Five cloud services are supported, "
"plus three local storage options."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;'s Add Address Book संवादः । पञ्च मेघसेवाः समर्थिताः सन्ति, अपि च "
"त्रयः स्थानीयभण्डारणविकल्पाः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose one of the options that appear in the dialog. Several of these "
"options link to data collections residing in the cloud: <glossterm linkend="
"\"gloss-dav\"><acronym>DAV</acronym></glossterm> groupware (Distributed "
"Authoring and Versioning, RFC4918), Google Contacts (your gmail.com "
"account), <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-kolab\">Kolab</glossterm> &nbsp;"
"groupware server (collaboration via <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-imap\">&IMAP;"
"</glossterm>), &Microsoft; Exchange Server <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-ews"
"\">EWS</glossterm> &nbsp;(Exchange Web Services, on servers running MS "
"software), and <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-group\">Open-Xchange &nbsp;"
"Groupware &nbsp;Server</glossterm> &nbsp;&nbsp;(an open-source alternative "
"to MS EWS). If you already have access to one or more of these cloud-based "
"resources, you can integrate those data into &nbsp;&kaddressbook; by simply "
"selecting the option and then entering your login credentials."
msgstr ""
"संवादे दृश्यमानेषु विकल्पेषु एकं चिनोतु । एतेषु कतिपये विकल्पाः मेघे निवसन्तः आँकडासंग्रहैः सह "
"लिङ्क् कुर्वन्ति: <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-dav\"><acronym>DAV</acronym></"
"glossterm> groupware (वितरितलेखनं संस्करणीकरणं च, RFC4918), Google सम्पर्कः (भवतः "
"gmail .com खाता), <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-kolab\">कोलाब</glossterm> &nbsp;"
"समूहवेयर सर्वर (<glossterm linkend=\"gloss-imap\">&IMAP;</glossterm> मार्गेण "
"सहकार्यम्), &Microsoft; Exchange Server <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-ews\">EWS</"
"glossterm> &nbsp;(एक्सचेंज जालसेवा, MS सॉफ्टवेयर चालितसर्वरेषु), तथा च <glossterm "
"linkend=\"gloss-group\">Open-Xchange &nbsp;समूहवेयर &nbsp; सर्वर</glossterm> "
"&nbsp;&nbsp;(MS EWS इत्यस्य मुक्त-स्रोत-विकल्पः) । यदि भवतः पूर्वमेव एतेषु मेघ-आधारित-"
"संसाधनेषु एकं वा अधिकं वा अभिगमः अस्ति तर्हि भवान् तान् दत्तांशान् &nbsp;&kaddressbook; "
"केवलं विकल्पं चित्वा ततः स्वस्य प्रवेशप्रमाणपत्रं प्रविष्ट्वा ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The remaining options in the dialog (Personal Contacts, vCard Directory, and "
"vCard File) all create data sets that are saved on a local storage device. "
"Each one of these options uses the same data format (<filename class="
"\"extension\">.vcf</filename>, or Virtual Card Format), the only difference "
"being in which particular directory the data are saved. The <quote>Personal "
"Contacts</quote> and <quote>vCard Directory</quote> options create a "
"separate file for each named contact you save; the <quote>vCard File</quote> "
"option puts all the data into one file. It's probably easiest to start with "
"the pre-defined <quote>Personal Contacts</quote> address book. You will not "
"need more address books unless you have extensive contact lists you would "
"like to keep separate."
msgstr ""
"संवादे अवशिष्टाः विकल्पाः (व्यक्तिगतसम्पर्काः, vCard निर्देशिका, vCard सञ्चिका च) सर्वे "
"आँकडासमूहान् निर्मान्ति ये स्थानीयभण्डारणयन्त्रे रक्षिताः भवन्ति । एतेषु प्रत्येकं विकल्पं समानं "
"दत्तांशस्वरूपं (<filename class=\"extension\">.vcf</filename>, अथवा Virtual Card "
"Format) उपयुज्यते, केवलं भेदः अस्ति यत् दत्तांशः कस्मिन् विशेषे निर्देशिकायां रक्षितः भवति "
"<quote>व्यक्तिगतसम्पर्क</quote> तथा <quote>vCard निर्देशिका</quote> विकल्पाः भवता "
"रक्षितस्य प्रत्येकस्य नामकस्य सम्पर्कस्य कृते पृथक् सञ्चिकां निर्मान्ति; <quote>vCard File</"
"quote> विकल्पः सर्वाणि दत्तांशं एकस्मिन् सञ्चिकायां स्थापयति । सम्भवतः पूर्वनिर्धारितेन "
"<quote>व्यक्तिगतसम्पर्क</quote> पतापुस्तिकायाः आरम्भः सर्वाधिकं सुलभः अस्ति । यावत् भवतः "
"विस्तृताः सम्पर्कसूचिकाः न सन्ति तावत् भवतः अधिकानां पतापुस्तकानां आवश्यकता न भविष्यति।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you have made your selection, click on OK. If you have selected a "
"<glossterm linkend=\"gloss-cloud\">cloud-based service</glossterm> a brief "
"dialog will ensue, to establish communications between <glossterm linkend="
"\"gloss-akonadi\">&akonadi;</glossterm> (the &PIM; cross-desktop storage "
"service) and the selected cloud server. Here's what the dialog looks like "
"for a Google (gmail.com) account. The other cloud-based services are "
"slightly different, but similar."
msgstr ""
"एकवारं भवता चयनं कृत्वा OK इत्यत्र क्लिक् कुर्वन्तु । यदि भवान् <glossterm linkend="
"\"gloss-cloud\">मेघाधारितसेवा</glossterm> चिनोति तर्हि संक्षिप्तः संवादः भविष्यति, "
"<glossterm linkend=\"gloss-akonadi\">&akonadi;</glossterm> ( &PIM; अत्र "
"Google (gmail.com) खातेः संवादः कीदृशः दृश्यते । अन्ये मेघाधारितसेवाः किञ्चित् भिन्नाः, "
"परन्तु समानाः सन्ति ।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail dialog</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail संवाद</screeninfo> इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट्"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail संवाद</phrase> इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail dialog. Begin by clicking <quote>Add</quote>. "
"A new dialog will appear. Once your credentials have been accepted, this "
"screen will reappear, and you will click &nbsp;<guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;"
"OK&nbsp;</guibutton>. If you would like &kaddressbook; to refresh the "
"locally cached copy of your contact list automatically, do it here, before "
"you click &nbsp;<guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;OK&nbsp;</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail संवादः । <quote>Add</quote> इत्यत्र क्लिक् कृत्वा "
"आरभत । नूतनः संवादः दृश्यते । एकदा भवतः प्रमाणपत्राणि स्वीकृतानि भवन्ति तदा एतत् पटलं "
"पुनः प्रकटितं भविष्यति, ततः भवन्तः &nbsp;<guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;ठीकम्&nbsp;</"
"guibutton> नुदन्ति । यदि भवान् इच्छति &kaddressbook; स्वसम्पर्कसूचिकायाः स्थानीयतया "
"संग्रहीतप्रतिलिपिं स्वयमेव ताजगीं कर्तुं, अत्र कुर्वन्तु, &nbsp;<guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;"
"ठीकम्&nbsp;</guibutton> क्लिक् कर्तुं पूर्वं ।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A second screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail dialog</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail संवादस्य द्वितीयः स्क्रीनशॉट्</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A second screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail dialog</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य लिङ्क्-टू-जीमेल-संवादस्य द्वितीयः स्क्रीनशॉट्</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another picture of &kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail dialog. Enter your gmail."
"com address and click <guibutton>&nbsp;Next&nbsp;</guibutton>. You will be "
"asked to enter your gmail password."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य link-to-gmail संवादस्य अन्यत् चित्रम् । स्वस्य gmail.com पतां "
"प्रविश्य <guibutton>&nbsp;अनन्तरं&nbsp;</guibutton> नुदन्तु । भवन्तः स्वस्य gmail "
"गुप्तशब्दं प्रविष्टुं प्रार्थयिष्यन्ति।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A third screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail dialog</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य लिङ्क्-टू-जीमेल-संवादस्य तृतीयः स्क्रीनशॉट्</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A third screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail dialog</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य लिङ्क्-टू-जीमेल-संवादस्य तृतीयः स्क्रीनशॉट्</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yet another picture of &kaddressbook;'s link-to-gmail dialog. Your account "
"name and password have been accepted by Google's server. Read the privacy "
"notice and press <guibutton>&nbsp;Allow&nbsp;</guibutton>, then "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;OK&nbsp;</guibutton> in the <quote>&nbsp;Add&nbsp;</"
"quote> dialog with which you started."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य link-to-gmail संवादस्य अपरं चित्रम् । भवतः खातेः नाम गुप्तशब्दः "
"च Google इत्यस्य सर्वरेण स्वीकृतम् अस्ति । गोपनीयतासूचना पठित्वा <guibutton>&nbsp;"
"अनुमन्यताम्&nbsp;</guibutton> नुदन्तु, ततः <quote>&nbsp;Add&nbsp;</quote> संवादे "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;ठीकम्&nbsp;</guibutton> नुदन्तु येन सह भवन्तः आरंभित।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter your login credentials as illustrated above and say OK. Voila! Your "
"cloud-based contact list is now integrated into &kaddressbook;."
msgstr ""
"उपरि यथा दर्शितं तथा स्वस्य प्रवेशप्रमाणपत्रं प्रविश्य ठीकम् इति वदन्तु । वोइला ! भवतः "
"मेघाधारितसम्पर्कसूची अधुना &kaddressbook;."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:272
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>The &kaddressbook; window after a gmail.com account has been "
"added.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>The &kaddressbook; gmail.com खातेः योजितस्य अनन्तरं विण्डो ।</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>The &kaddressbook; window after a gmail.com account has been added.</"
"phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>The &kaddressbook; gmail.com खातेः योजितस्य अनन्तरं window ।</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another picture of the &nbsp;&kaddressbook; window, after a gmail.com "
"account has been added. You can now manipulate your gmail contacts via "
"&kaddressbook;, if you like."
msgstr ""
"अन्यत् चित्रं &nbsp;&kaddressbook; window, gmail.com खातं योजितस्य अनन्तरम् । इदानीं "
"भवान् इच्छति चेत् &kaddressbook;, मार्गेण स्वस्य gmail सम्पर्कं परिवर्तयितुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As the preceding screenshot indicates, once you have registered "
"&kaddressbook; as a trusted resource, you can view and edit your gmail "
"contacts using &kaddressbook;. Of course, you may also continue to maintain "
"your contacts by using a web browser, if you wish."
msgstr ""
"यथा पूर्वस्मिन् स्क्रीनशॉट् सूचयति, एकवारं पञ्जीकरणं कृत्वा &kaddressbook; "
"विश्वसनीयसंसाधनरूपेण, भवान् &kaddressbook; इत्यस्य उपयोगेन स्वस्य gmail सम्पर्कं द्रष्टुं "
"सम्पादयितुं च शक्नोति । अवश्यं, भवान् इच्छति चेत् जालपुटस्य उपयोगेन अपि स्वसम्पर्कं निरन्तरं "
"कर्तुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you selected one of the local address book options in <link linkend="
"\"select-a-format-step\">step 2</link> above, a different dialog will ensue."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् स्थानीयपतेःपुस्तिकाविकल्पेषु एकं चिनोति<link linkend=\"select-a-format-step"
"\"> चरण 2</link> उपरि, भिन्नः संवादः भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Personal Contacts</"
"quote> dialog.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>व्यक्तिगतसम्पर्क</quote> संवादस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् "
"।</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:313
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Personal Contacts</quote> "
"dialog.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>व्यक्तिगतसम्पर्क</quote> संवादस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् ।</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Personal Contacts</quote> dialog. You may specify "
"which directory will contain your data, and whether you have write access to "
"this resource, or not. For most people, the default selections (as shown "
"above) work well."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>व्यक्तिगतसम्पर्क</quote> संवादः । भवान् निर्दिष्टुं शक्नोति यत् "
"कस्मिन् निर्देशिकायां भवतः दत्तांशः भविष्यति, तथा च भवतः अस्मिन् संसाधने लेखनप्रवेशः अस्ति "
"वा न वा । अधिकांशजनानां कृते पूर्वनिर्धारितचयनं (यथा उपरि दर्शितम्) सम्यक् कार्यं करोति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Make any modifications you deem necessary in the <quote>Personal Contacts</"
"quote> dialog, then click <guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;OK&nbsp;</guibutton>. A "
"new address book will appear in the main &kaddressbook; interface window, as "
"shown below."
msgstr ""
"<quote>व्यक्तिगतसम्पर्क</quote> संवादे यत्किमपि परिवर्तनं भवता आवश्यकं मन्यते तत् कुरुत, ततः "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;ठीकम्&nbsp;</guibutton> नुदन्तु । मुख्ये &kaddressbook; "
"interface window, यथा अधः दर्शितम् ।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s main window with an empty "
"<quote>Personal Contacts</quote> address book.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य मुख्यविण्डो इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् रिक्तेन "
"<quote>व्यक्तिगतसम्पर्क</quote> पतापुस्तकेन सह ।</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s main window with an empty "
"<quote>Personal Contacts</quote> address book.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य मुख्यविण्डो इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् रिक्तेन "
"<quote>व्यक्तिगतसम्पर्क</quote> पतापुस्तकेन सह ।</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:343
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s main window after the <quote>Personal Contacts</quote> "
"address book has been re-created."
msgstr ""
"<quote>व्यक्तिगतसम्पर्क</quote> पतापुस्तकस्य पुनः निर्मितस्य अनन्तरं &kaddressbook; "
"इत्यस्य मुख्यविण्डो ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Add a New Contact"
msgstr "नूतनं सम्पर्कं कथं योजयितव्यम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open &kaddressbook;'s New Contact dialog by clicking the <guibutton>&nbsp;"
"&plus;&nbsp;New Contact&nbsp;</guibutton> button on the Toolbar. A dialog "
"box will appear."
msgstr ""
"साधनपट्टिकायां <guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;नवसम्पर्कः&nbsp;</guibutton> बटनं "
"क्लिक् कृत्वा &kaddressbook; इत्यस्य नूतनसम्पर्कसंवादं उद्घाटयन्तु । संवादपेटिका दृश्यते ।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:366 index.docbook:683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>New Contact</quote> "
"dialog.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>नवसम्पर्कस्य</quote> संवादस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् ।</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:372 index.docbook:689
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>New Contact</quote> dialog.</"
"phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>नवसम्पर्क</quote> संवादस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् ।</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>New Contact</quote> dialog after clicking the "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;New Contact&nbsp;</guibutton> button on the "
"Toolbar."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>नवसम्पर्कः</quote> संवादः साधनपट्टिकायां "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;नवसम्पर्कः&nbsp;</guibutton> इति बटनं क्लिक् कृत्वा ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:386
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As you can see from the preceding screenshot, the <quote>New Contact</quote> "
"dialog allows one to enter several different data items. Additional data may "
"be entered via the <quote>Location</quote>, <quote>Business</quote>, "
"<quote>Personal</quote>, <quote>Notes</quote>, <quote>Custom Fields</quote>, "
"and <quote>Crypto Settings</quote> sub-dialogs, as explained more fully in "
"<link linkend=\"editing-contact-data\">chapter 4</link>, below. For now, "
"let's concentrate on adding the <quote>Contact</quote> data items appearing "
"in the preceding illustration."
msgstr ""
"यथा पूर्वं स्क्रीनशॉट् तः द्रष्टुं शक्नुवन्ति, the...<quote> नया सम्पर्क</quote> dialog "
"इत्यनेन अनेकाः भिन्नाः data items प्रविष्टुं शक्यन्ते । अतिरिक्तदत्तांशः मार्गेण प्रविष्टः "
"भवितुम् अर्हति<quote> स्थानीय</quote> , ९.<quote> व्यवसायः</quote> , ९.<quote> "
"व्यक्तिगत</quote> , ९.<quote> टिप्पणियाँ</quote> , ९.<quote> कस्टम फील्ड्स</"
"quote> , तथा<quote> क्रिप्टो सेटिंग्स्</quote> उपसंवादाः, यथा अधिकं पूर्णतया व्याख्यातं "
"in<link linkend=\"editing-contact-data\"> अध्याय 4</link> , अधः। इदानीं कृते "
"योजयितुं एकाग्रतां कुर्मः<quote> संपर्कः</quote> पूर्वचित्रे दृश्यमानानि दत्तांशवस्तूनि।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have created more than one address book, use the drop-down list "
"labeled <quote>Add to:</quote> to select the data set to which the new "
"contact will be added. Then enter the new contact's name in the input field "
"marked <quote>Name</quote>, and key in his or her email address in the input "
"field labeled &nbsp;<quote>Email</quote>. If you want to specify special "
"formatting options for this contact's name data, click the "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;...&nbsp;</guibutton> button to the right of the "
"<quote>Name</quote> input field and follow the prompts. If you wish to add "
"more email addresses for this person, click the <guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;"
"</guibutton> button to the right of the <quote>Email</quote> input field and "
"another Email input field will be generated. To delete an Email address, "
"click the associated <guibutton>&nbsp;&minus;&nbsp;</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् एकादशाधिकं पतापुस्तकं निर्मितवान् तर्हि <quote>Add to:</quote> इति "
"लेबलयुक्तस्य ड्रॉप्-डाउन-सूचिकायाः उपयोगं कृत्वा यस्मिन् दत्तांशसमूहे नूतनः सम्पर्कः योजितः "
"भविष्यति तस्य चयनं कुर्वन्तु । ततः <quote>नाम</quote> इति चिह्निते निवेशक्षेत्रे "
"नूतनसम्पर्कस्य नाम प्रविशन्तु, &nbsp;<quote>ईमेल</quote> इति लेबलयुक्ते निवेशक्षेत्रे तस्य ईमेल-"
"सङ्केतं कुञ्जीकृत्य स्थापयन्तु यदि भवान् अस्य सम्पर्कस्य नामदत्तांशस्य कृते विशेषस्वरूपणविकल्पान् "
"निर्दिष्टुं इच्छति तर्हि <quote>नाम</quote> निवेशक्षेत्रस्य दक्षिणभागे "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;...&nbsp;</guibutton> बटनं नुदतु तथा च संकेतानां अनुसरणं कुर्वन्तु . "
"यदि भवान् अस्य व्यक्तिस्य कृते अधिकानि ईमेल-सङ्केतानि योजयितुम् इच्छति तर्हि <quote>Email</"
"quote> निवेशक्षेत्रस्य दक्षिणभागे <guibutton>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</guibutton> बटनं नुदतु "
"अन्यत् Email निवेशक्षेत्रं भविष्यति उत्पन्नः । ईमेल-सङ्केतं विलोपयितुं, तत्सम्बद्धं "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;&minus;&nbsp;</guibutton> बटनं नुदन्तु ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may also associate a nickname, one or more telephone numbers, multiple "
"instant messaging services, and several web sites with each contact in an "
"address book, as explained in <link linkend=\"editing-contact-data\">chapter "
"4</link>. You may also use the <quote>Show messages ...</quote> and "
"<quote>Allow remote content ...</quote> options to fine-tune the way &kmail; "
"handles email you receive from each contact. See <link linkend=\"integration-"
"with-other-kde-programs\">chapter 3</link> for a more complete explanation."
msgstr ""
"भवन्तः पतापुस्तके प्रत्येकं सम्पर्केन सह उपनाम, एकं वा अधिकं दूरभाषसङ्ख्यां, बहुविधं "
"तत्क्षणसन्देशसेवा, अनेकजालस्थलानि च सम्बद्धं कर्तुं शक्नुवन्ति, यथा व्याख्यातं<link linkend="
"\"editing-contact-data\"> अध्याय 4</link> . भवन्तः अपि उपयोक्तुं शक्नुवन्ति<quote> "
"सन्देशान् दर्शयतु ...</quote> तथा<quote> दूरस्थसामग्रीम् अनुमन्यताम् ...</quote> मार्गं "
"सूक्ष्मरूपेण स्थापयितुं विकल्पाः &amp;kmail; प्रत्येकं सम्पर्कात् भवन्तः प्राप्तं ईमेलं सम्पादयति। "
"पश्यतु<link linkend=\"integration-with-other-kde-programs\"> अध्याय 3</link> "
"अधिकसम्पूर्णव्याख्यानार्थम् ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:424
#, no-c-format
msgid "Integration With Other &kde; Programs"
msgstr "अन्यैः सह एकीकरणं &kde; कार्यक्रमाः"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid "Integration Overview -- &kmail;"
msgstr "एकीकरणस्य अवलोकनम् -- &kmail;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:429
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Because &kaddressbook; -- an essential piece of &PIM;, &kde;'s suite of "
"Personal Information Management programs -- is the central repository for "
"information about all your contacts, it has been integrated into &nbsp;"
"&kmail; and also into &korganizer;. Here is a quick look at the interface "
"between &kaddressbook; and those two programs."
msgstr ""
"यतः &kaddressbook; -- &PIM;, &kde; इत्यस्य व्यक्तिगतसूचनाप्रबन्धनकार्यक्रमानाम् एकः "
"आवश्यकः भागः -- भवतः सर्वेषां सम्पर्कानाम् विषये सूचनानां केन्द्रीयभण्डारः अस्ति, एतत् &nbsp;"
"&kmail; तथा &korganizer; इत्यत्र अपि । अत्र &kaddressbook; तथा ताभ्यां कार्यक्रमौ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:436
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting &kaddressbook; from &kmail;'s Tools Menu"
msgstr "आरभ्य &kaddressbook; &kmail;'s Tools Menu इत्यस्मात्"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:440
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kmail;'s <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Address Book</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option.</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kmail;इत्यस्य <menuchoice><guimenu>उपकरण</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>पतापुस्तक</guimenuitem></menuchoice> विकल्पस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् ।</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:446
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kmail;'s <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Address Book</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&kmail;इत्यस्य <menuchoice><guimenu>उपकरण</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>पतापुस्तक</guimenuitem></menuchoice> विकल्पस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् ।</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Launching &kaddressbook; from &kmail;'s <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"address-book-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Address Book</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu choice."
msgstr ""
"प्रारम्भं कुर्वन् &kaddressbook; &kmail;'s <menuchoice><guimenu>उपकरणात्</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"address-book-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject>< /"
"inlinemediaobject>पतेः पुस्तकम्</guimenuitem></menuchoice> मेनू विकल्पः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:458
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This interface is the epitome of simplicity. Need to consult or update the "
"entry for one of your contacts while reading or composing an email message "
"with &kmail;? Left click <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"address-book-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Address Book</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, and the "
"&kaddressbook; application will be launched automatically, allowing quick "
"access to the contact data you want to view or modify."
msgstr ""
"अयं अन्तरफलकः सरलतायाः प्रतिरूपः अस्ति । &kmail;? वामक्लिक् "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>उपकरणं</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"address-book-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> "
"इति पतापुस्तिका</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>, तथा च &kaddressbook; अनुप्रयोगः "
"स्वयमेव प्रारभ्यते, येन भवन्तः द्रष्टुम् अथवा परिवर्तयितुम् इच्छन्ति सम्पर्कदत्तांशस्य शीघ्रं प्रवेशं "
"प्राप्नुवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:469
#, no-c-format
msgid "Querying &kaddressbook; from &kmail;'s Message Composition Window"
msgstr "प्रश्नं कुर्वन् &kaddressbook; &kmail;'s Message Composition Window इत्यस्मात्"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of auto completion from inside &kmail;'s message "
"composition window.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kmail; इत्यस्य सन्देशरचनाविण्डो इत्यस्य अन्तः स्वतः समाप्तेः स्क्रीनशॉट् ।</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:479
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of auto completion from inside &kmail;'s message "
"composition window.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&kmail; इत्यस्य सन्देशरचनाविण्डो इत्यस्य अन्तः स्वतः समाप्तेः स्क्रीनशॉट् ।</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using &kaddressbook;'s auto completion feature from inside &kmail;'s message "
"composition window."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; इत्यस्य सन्देशरचनाविण्डो इत्यस्य अन्तः &kaddressbook; इत्यस्य स्वतः "
"समाप्तिविशेषतायाः उपयोगः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are composing a new email message, &kmail; helps you find the "
"recipient's complete email address by presenting a list of probable matches "
"drawn from the contents of &kaddressbook; and from your email archives, as "
"illustrated above. Just left click an item in the list to use that email "
"address."
msgstr ""
"यदा भवान् नूतनं ईमेलसन्देशं रचयति तदा &kmail; &kaddressbook; तथा च भवतः ईमेल-आर्काइव्-"
"तः, यथा उपरि दृष्टान्तः । तस्य ईमेल-सङ्केतस्य उपयोगाय केवलं सूचीस्थं किमपि द्रव्यं वाम-क्लिक् "
"कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmail;'s Recipient Selection Dialog"
msgstr "&kmail;'s प्राप्तकर्ता चयनसंवादः"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of the recipient selection dialog inside &kmail;'s "
"message composition window.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kmail; इत्यस्य सन्देशरचनाविण्डो इत्यस्य अन्तः प्राप्तकर्ताचयनसंवादस्य "
"स्क्रीनशॉट् ।</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:509
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of the recipient selection dialog inside &kmail;'s "
"message composition window.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&kmail; इत्यस्य सन्देशरचनाविण्डो इत्यस्य अन्तः प्राप्तकर्ताचयनसंवादस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् ।"
"</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting multiple addressees with the recipient selection dialog inside "
"&nbsp;&kmail;'s message composition window."
msgstr "&nbsp;&kmail;इत्यस्य सन्देशरचनाविण्डोमध्ये प्राप्तकर्ताचयनसंवादेन सह बहुसंबोधकचयनम् ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:520
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are addressing a new email message to multiple recipients, &kmail; "
"provides a convenient method of choosing multiple addressees from the "
"contacts you have saved with &kaddressbook;. Simply left click the "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;Select ...&nbsp;</guibutton> button to open a Drop Down Box "
"that lists all the contacts in the selected address books. Then scroll "
"through the list (or use the handy <quote>Search:</quote> box), select the "
"recipient you want, and left click &nbsp;<guibutton>&nbsp;Add as To&nbsp;</"
"guibutton>, <guibutton>&nbsp;Add as CC&nbsp;</guibutton>, or "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;Add as BCC&nbsp;</guibutton> to add this person to the list "
"of email recipients for your new message. Choose <guibutton>&nbsp;Add as "
"Reply-To&nbsp;</guibutton> to insert this address into your message as a "
"<quote>Reply To</quote> tag."
msgstr ""
"यदा भवान् बहुभ्यः प्राप्तिभ्यः नूतनं ईमेल-सन्देशं सम्बोधयति तदा &kmail; भवता "
"&kaddressbook; इत्यनेन सह रक्षितानां सम्पर्कानाम् एकाधिकपतेः चयनस्य सुविधाजनकपद्धतिः "
"प्रदाति । केवलं <guibutton>&nbsp;Select ...&nbsp;</guibutton> बटनं वाम-क्लिक् कृत्वा "
"एकं Drop Down Box उद्घाटयितुं यत् चयनित-सङ्केत-पुस्तकेषु सर्वान् सम्पर्कानाम् सूचीं ददाति । "
"ततः सूचीं स्क्रॉल कुर्वन्तु (अथवा सुलभं <quote>अन्वेषणम्:</quote> पेटीम् उपयुज्यताम्), इच्छितं "
"प्राप्तकं चिनोतु, &nbsp;<guibutton>&nbsp;Add as To&nbsp;</guibutton>, "
"<guibutton> इति वामक्लिक् कुर्वन्तु &nbsp;CC&nbsp;</guibutton>रूपेण योजयतु, अथवा "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;यथा योजयतु BCC&nbsp;</guibutton> इत्येतत् व्यक्तिं भवतः नूतनसन्देशस्य "
"कृते ईमेलग्राहकसूचौ योजयितुं । <quote>Reply To</quote> टैग् इति रूपेण स्वसन्देशे एतत् पतां "
"सम्मिलितुं <guibutton>&nbsp;Add as Reply-To&nbsp;</guibutton> इति चिनोतु ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kmail;'s New Contact Creation Interface"
msgstr "&kmail;'s New Contact Creation Interface"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:538
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of the new contact creation interface inside "
"&kmail;'s message viewing window.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kmail; इत्यस्य सन्देशदर्शनविण्डो इत्यस्य अन्तः नूतनसम्पर्कनिर्माण-अन्तरफलकस्य "
"स्क्रीनशॉट् ।</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of the new contact creation interface inside &kmail;'s "
"message viewing window.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&kmail; इत्यस्य सन्देशदर्शनविण्डो इत्यस्य अन्तः नूतनसम्पर्कनिर्माण-अन्तरफलकस्य "
"स्क्रीनशॉट् ।</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Invoking the new contact creation dialog from &kmail;'s message viewing "
"window."
msgstr "&kmail; इत्यस्य सन्देशदर्शनविण्डोतः नूतनसम्पर्कनिर्माणसंवादं आह्वयति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:554
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you receive an email message from someone who is not yet in your "
"address book, &kmail; makes it very easy to create a new contact. Simply "
"point your cursor at the email address you want to save, then click the "
"&RMB; and a context menu will appear (see above). Select <guimenuitem>&nbsp;"
"&plus; Add to Address Book&nbsp;</guimenuitem> to add the selected email "
"address to one of your address books. If you recognize this person as "
"somebody who's already in your address book, and he is using a new email "
"address, you may click on <guimenuitem>&nbsp;&plus; Add to Existing "
"Contact&nbsp;</guimenuitem> instead -- this enters a dialog that will direct "
"&nbsp;&kaddressbook; to the spot where you want to insert the new email "
"address."
msgstr ""
"यदा भवन्तः कस्यचित् ईमेल-सन्देशं प्राप्नुवन्ति यः अद्यापि भवतः पतापुस्तिकायां नास्ति, तदा "
"&kmail; नूतनं सम्पर्कं निर्मातुं अतीव सुलभं करोति। केवलं भवता रक्षितुम् इच्छितं ईमेल-सङ्केतं स्वस्य "
"कर्सरं दर्शयतु, ततः &RMB; तथा च सन्दर्भमेनू दृश्यते (ऊर्ध्वं पश्यन्तु) । <guimenuitem>&nbsp;"
"&plus; चयनितं ईमेल-सङ्केतं भवतः एकस्मिन् पतापुस्तके योजयितुं पतापुस्तके&nbsp;</guimenuitem> "
"मध्ये योजयतु । यदि भवान् एतत् व्यक्तिं कश्चन भवतः पतापुस्तके पूर्वमेव अस्ति इति ज्ञायते, सः च "
"नूतनं ईमेल-सङ्केतं उपयुज्यते, तर्हि भवान् <guimenuitem>&nbsp;&plus; तस्य स्थाने "
"विद्यमानसम्पर्कं योजयन्तु&nbsp;</guimenuitem> -- एतत् एकं संवादं प्रविशति यत् &nbsp;"
"&kaddressbook; यत्र भवन्तः नूतनं ईमेल-सङ्केतं सम्मिलितुं इच्छन्ति तत्र गच्छन्तु ।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:564
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of the ensuing new contact creation dialog.</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>अनुवर्तमानस्य नूतनसम्पर्कनिर्माणसंवादस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् ।</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of the ensuing new contact creation dialog.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>अनुवर्तमानस्य नूतनसम्पर्कनिर्माणसंवादस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् ।</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:573
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choosing the address book in which the new contact will be created."
msgstr "यस्मिन् पतापुस्तिकायां नूतनः सम्पर्कः निर्मितः भविष्यति तस्य चयनम्।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; will ask you to choose the address book to which the new contact "
"should be added."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; यस्मिन् पतापुस्तके नूतनः सम्पर्कः योजितव्यः तत् पतापुस्तकं चिन्वतु इति भवन्तं वक्ष्यति।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>Another screenshot of the ensuing new contact creation dialog.</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>अनुवर्तमानस्य नूतनसम्पर्कनिर्माणसंवादस्य अन्यः स्क्रीनशॉट् ।</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:591
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>Another screenshot of the ensuing new contact creation dialog.</"
"phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>अनन्तरं नूतनसम्पर्कनिर्माणसंवादस्य अन्यः स्क्रीनशॉटः ।</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:594
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Deciding if you would like to edit the newly created contact now, or later."
msgstr "नूतननिर्मितं सम्पर्कं सम्पादयितुम् इच्छति वा इदानीं, पश्चात् वा इति निर्णयः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:601
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kmail; will also ask you if you wish to <link linkend=\"editing-contact-data"
"\"> edit the new contact</link> &nbsp;that has just been added. Say "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;Yes&nbsp;</guibutton> if you want to add more data "
"to the new entry right away."
msgstr ""
"&amp;kmail; इच्छसि वा इति अपि पृच्छति<link linkend=\"editing-contact-data\"> "
"नूतनं सम्पर्कं सम्पादयन्तु</link> तत् अधुना एव योजितम् अस्ति। कथय<guibutton> ✔ हाँ</"
"guibutton> यदि भवान् तत्क्षणमेव नूतनप्रविष्टौ अधिकदत्तांशं योजयितुम् इच्छति।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kaddressbook;'s Interface with &korganizer;"
msgstr "&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य &korganizer;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:613
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&korganizer;, the &kde; scheduling and calendar management program, allows "
"you to send e-mail messages to people you want to invite to a meeting, and "
"provides two interfaces with &kaddressbook; in this connection."
msgstr ""
"&korganizer;, इति &kde; समयनिर्धारणं तथा पञ्चाङ्गप्रबन्धनकार्यक्रमः, भवान् सभायां "
"आमन्त्रयितुं इच्छति जनानां कृते ई-मेलसन्देशान् प्रेषयितुं शक्नोति, तथा च &kaddressbook; अस्मिन् "
"सन्दर्भे ।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:620 index.docbook:643
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s attendees tab.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&korganizer; इत्यस्य उपस्थितानां ट्याब् इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् ।</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:626
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>A screenshot of &korganizer;'s attendees tab.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&korganizer; इत्यस्य उपस्थितानां ट्याब् इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् ।</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:629
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding a single attendee to a scheduled meeting in &nbsp;&korganizer;."
msgstr "&nbsp;&korganizer; इत्यस्मिन् निर्धारितसमागमे एकं उपस्थितं योजयित्वा।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:636
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first interface is just like the <link linkend=\"autocompletion-feature-"
"on-new-email\">auto completion feature</link> provided by &kmail;: just "
"start typing the name of the person you want to invite, and you will be "
"presented with a list of probable matches, as illustrated above."
msgstr ""
"प्रथमं अन्तरफलकं यथा...<link linkend=\"autocompletion-feature-on-new-email\"> "
"स्वतः समाप्तिविशेषता</link> provided by &amp;kmail;: केवलं यस्य व्यक्तिस्य नाम टङ्कयितुं "
"आरभत यस्य भवन्तः आमन्त्रयितुं इच्छन्ति, ततः भवन्तः सम्भाव्यमेलनानां सूचीं प्रस्तुतं भविष्यन्ति, "
"यथा उपरि चित्रितम् ।"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:649
#, no-c-format
msgid "&korganizer;'s attendees tab."
msgstr "&korganizer;'s attendees ट्याब्."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:652
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding multiple attendees to a scheduled meeting in &nbsp;&korganizer;."
msgstr "&nbsp;&korganizer; इत्यस्मिन् निर्धारितसभायां बहुविधं उपस्थितं योजयित्वा ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:659
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The second interface is just like the <link linkend=\"recipient-selection-"
"dialog\">recipient selection dialog</link> &nbsp;provided by &kmail;: when "
"you left click the <guibutton>&nbsp;Select Attendees ...&nbsp;</guibutton> "
"button, a searchable list of the contacts in all your address books will "
"appear, as the preceding screenshot shows."
msgstr ""
"द्वितीयं अन्तरफलकं यथा अस्ति<link linkend=\"recipient-selection-dialog\"> "
"प्राप्तकर्ता चयनसंवादः</link> provided by &amp;kmail;: यदा भवन्तः वामतः क्लिक् "
"कुर्वन्ति तदा...<guibutton> उपस्थितानां चयनं कुर्वन्तु ...</guibutton> बटन्, भवतः सर्वेषु "
"पतापुस्तकेषु सम्पर्कस्य अन्वेषणीयसूची दृश्यते, यथा पूर्वस्मिन् स्क्रीनशॉट् दर्शयति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:668
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding or Editing Contact Data"
msgstr "सम्पर्कदत्तांशं योजयितुं वा सम्पादयितुं वा"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:671
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Basics"
msgstr "मूलभूताः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:673
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you first click on the "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Add Contact&nbsp;&nbsp;"
"</guibutton> button on &kaddressbook;'s Toolbar, this screen will appear. "
"(If you click on <guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"document-edit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Edit Contact&nbsp;&nbsp;</guibutton>, a similar screen "
"appears, the only difference being that the drop-down box labeled <quote>Add "
"to:</quote> will not appear as part of the <quote>Edit</quote> dialog. That "
"is why both functions are covered in this chapter: they're practically "
"identical.)"
msgstr ""
"यदा प्रथमवारं <guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>सम्पर्कं "
"योजयतु&nbsp;&nbsp;</guibutton> इत्यत्र क्लिक् करोति &kaddressbook;'s Toolbar "
"इत्यत्र बटनं कुर्वन्तु, एतत् पटलं दृश्यते । (यदि भवान् "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-"
"edit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>सम्पर्क "
"सम्पादयतु&nbsp;&nbsp;</guibutton> इत्यत्र क्लिक् करोति तर्हि तथैव पटलः दृश्यते, केवलं भेदः "
"अस्ति यत् <quote>Add to:</quote> इति लेबलयुक्तं ड्रॉप्-डाउन-पेटी भागरूपेण न दृश्यते "
"<quote>Edit</quote> संवादस्य अत एव अस्मिन् अध्याये उभयकार्यं आच्छादितम् अस्ति: ते "
"व्यावहारिकरूपेण समानाः सन्ति।)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:692
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Add Contact</quote> dialog after clicking the "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Add Contact&nbsp;&nbsp;"
"</guibutton> button on the Toolbar."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>सम्पर्कं योजयतु</quote> संवादं "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></ इत्यत्र क्लिक् कृत्वा "
"inlinemediaobject>उपकरणपट्टिकायां सम्पर्कं योजयन्तु&nbsp;&nbsp;</guibutton> बटनं "
"योजयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:703
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Contact Tab"
msgstr "सम्पर्क ट्याब् इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We have already seen (in <link linkend=\"how-to-add-a-new-contact\">How to "
"Add a New Contact</link>&nbsp;) how basic data like Name and Email are "
"entered when a new contact record is created. Here's a description of the "
"many ways to use the rest of the data fields accessible from the "
"<quote>Contact</quote> tab in the "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Add Contact&nbsp;&nbsp;"
"</guibutton> dialog."
msgstr ""
"अस्माभिः पूर्वमेव दृष्टम् (इन्<link linkend=\"how-to-add-a-new-contact\"> नूतनं सम्पर्कं "
"कथं योजयितव्यम्</link> ) यदा नूतनः सम्पर्क-अभिलेखः निर्मीयते तदा Name तथा Email "
"इत्यादीनि मूलभूत-दत्तांशं कथं प्रविष्टं भवति । अत्र तः अभिगम्यमानानां शेषदत्तांशक्षेत्राणां "
"उपयोगस्य अनेकमार्गाणां वर्णनम् अस्ति<quote> संपर्कः</quote> टब इत्यत्र "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> सम्पर्कं योजयतु</"
"guibutton> संवादः ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:713
#, no-c-format
msgid "Phone"
msgstr "फोनं"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:713
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may associate one or more telephone numbers with this person. Use the "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;</guibutton> and <guibutton>&nbsp;&minus;&nbsp;"
"</guibutton> buttons to add or delete phone number fields. The "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;Home<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-"
"down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton> "
"Drop Down Box allows you to identify fifteen categories of phone numbers "
"(Home, Work, Mobile, Car,<glossterm linkend=\"gloss-isdn\"> <acronym>ISDN</"
"acronym></glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-pcs\"><acronym>PCS</"
"acronym></glossterm>, &etc;)"
msgstr ""
"भवान् अस्मिन् व्यक्तिना सह एकं वा अधिकं वा दूरभाषसङ्ख्यां सम्बद्धं कर्तुं शक्नोति । "
"दूरभाषसङ्ख्याक्षेत्राणि योजयितुं विलोपयितुं वा <guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;</"
"guibutton> तथा <guibutton>&nbsp;&minus;&nbsp;</guibutton> बटन् इत्यस्य उपयोगं "
"कुर्वन्तु । <guibutton>&nbsp;Home<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"go-down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guibutton> ड्रॉप् डाउन पेटी भवन्तं परिचययितुं शक्नोति पञ्चदश श्रेणयः दूरभाषसङ्ख्याः (गृहं, "
"कार्यं, मोबाईल, कार,<glossterm linkend=\"gloss-isdn\"> <acronym>ISDN</"
"acronym></glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-pcs\"><acronym>पीसीएस</"
"acronym></glossterm>, इत्यादि)"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid "Messaging"
msgstr "सन्देशप्रसारणम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may associate one or more Instant Messaging service identities with this "
"person. Use the <guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;</guibutton> and "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;&minus;&nbsp;</guibutton> buttons to add or delete "
"messaging service fields. The <guibutton>&nbsp;Select ..."
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-down.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton> Drop Down Box "
"permits you to identify thirteen categories of IM services: <glossterm "
"linkend=\"gloss-aim\">AIM,</glossterm> Facebook, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-"
"gadu-gadu\">Gadu-Gadu</glossterm>, Google Talk, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-"
"gpws\">GroupWise</glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-icq\"><acronym>ICQ</"
"acronym></glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-irc\">&irc;</glossterm>, "
"<glossterm linkend=\"gloss-jabber\">Jabber</glossterm>, <glossterm linkend="
"\"gloss-mnwhl\">Meanwhile</glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-sms"
"\"><acronym>SMS</acronym></glossterm>, Skype, Twitter, and Yahoo. (MSN "
"Messenger is still on the list of IM services in version 5.10.3; it has been "
"defunct since 2014.)"
msgstr ""
"भवान् अस्मिन् व्यक्तिना सह एकं वा अधिकं वा Instant Messaging सेवापरिचयं सम्बद्धं कर्तुं "
"शक्नोति । सन्देशसेवाक्षेत्राणि योजयितुं विलोपयितुं वा <guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;</"
"guibutton> तथा <guibutton>&nbsp;&minus;&nbsp;</guibutton> बटन् इत्यस्य उपयोगं "
"कुर्वन्तु । <guibutton>&nbsp;चयनं ...<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"go-down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guibutton> Drop Down Box इत्यस्य अनुमतिः अस्ति भवन्तः IM सेवानां त्रयोदशवर्गान् "
"चिन्तयितुं शक्नुवन्ति: <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-aim\">AIM,</glossterm> Facebook, "
"<glossterm linkend=\"gloss-gadu-gadu\">गडु-गडु</glossterm>, गूगल टॉक, "
"<glossterm linkend=\"gloss-gpws\">समूहवाइज</glossterm>, <glossterm linkend="
"\"gloss-icq\">< acronym>ICQ</acronym></glossterm>, <glossterm linkend="
"\"gloss-irc\">&irc;</glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-jabber\">जब्बर</"
"glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-mnwhl\">इतर</glossterm>, <glossterm "
"linkend =\"gloss-sms\"><acronym>SMS</acronym></glossterm>, स्काइप्, ट्विटर, "
"तथा... याहू। (MSN Messenger अद्यापि ५.१०.३ संस्करणे IM सेवानां सूचीयां अस्ति; २०१४ तः "
"निष्क्रियः अस्ति ।)"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:733
#, no-c-format
msgid "<term>Web</term>"
msgstr "<term>जालम्</term>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:733
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may associate one or more web site &URL;s with this person. Use the "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;</guibutton> and <guibutton>&nbsp;&minus;&nbsp;"
"</guibutton> buttons to add or delete Web address fields. The "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;Select ...<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata "
"fileref=\"go-down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guibutton> Drop Down Box allows you to identify three different kinds of Web "
"addresses: Home, Work, and Other."
msgstr ""
"भवान् अस्मिन् व्यक्तिना सह एकं वा अधिकं वा जालस्थलं &URL;s सम्बद्धं कर्तुं शक्नोति। "
"जालसङ्केतक्षेत्राणि योजयितुं विलोपयितुं वा <guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;</guibutton> "
"तथा <guibutton>&nbsp;&minus;&nbsp;</guibutton> बटन् इत्यस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु । "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;चयनं ...<inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"go-down.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guibutton> ड्रॉप् डाउन बॉक्स अनुमन्यते you to identify three different kinds of "
"Web addresses: गृहं, कार्यम्, अन्यत् च ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:740
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tags"
msgstr "टैग्स"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:740
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may associate one or more Tags of your own devising with this person. "
"Use the <guibutton>&nbsp;...&nbsp;</guibutton> button to enter the Tag "
"creation and configuration dialog illustrated below."
msgstr ""
"भवान् स्वस्य कल्पितस्य एकं वा अधिकं वा Tags अस्मिन् व्यक्तिना सह सम्बद्धं कर्तुं शक्नोति। "
"अधोलिखितं Tag निर्माणं विन्याससंवादं च प्रविष्टुं <guibutton>&nbsp;...&nbsp;</"
"guibutton> बटनस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:749
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Tags</quote> dialog.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>टैग्स्</quote> संवादः ।</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:755
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Tags</quote> dialog.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>टैग्स्</quote> संवादः ।</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:758
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Manage Tags</quote> dialog after clicking the "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;...&nbsp;</guibutton> button next to <quote>Tags</quote>."
msgstr ""
"<quote>टैग्स्</quote> इत्यस्य पार्श्वे <guibutton>&nbsp;...&nbsp;</guibutton> बटन् "
"नुदनस्य अनन्तरं <quote>टैग्स् प्रबन्धयन्तु</quote> संवादः ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:768
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tags (continued)"
msgstr "टैग्स् (अन्तरम्)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:768
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guibutton>&nbsp;Create new tag&nbsp;</guibutton> button and the "
"data entry field to the left to build your customized list of tags. Select "
"the tags associated with this person from the list appearing in the "
"configuration window. Press the <guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;OK&nbsp;</guibutton> "
"button to add the selected tags to this contact."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton>&nbsp;नवटैग् रचयतु&nbsp;</guibutton> बटनं वामतः दत्तांशप्रविष्टिक्षेत्रं च "
"उपयुज्य स्वस्य अनुकूलितटैग्सूचीं निर्मातुम् । विन्यासविण्डो मध्ये दृश्यमानायाः सूचीतः अस्य "
"व्यक्तिस्य सह सम्बद्धानि टैग्स् चिनोतु । अस्मिन् सम्पर्के चयनितटैग्स् योजयितुं <guibutton>&nbsp;"
"✔&nbsp;OK&nbsp;</guibutton> बटनं नुदन्तु ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:774
#, no-c-format
msgid "Blog Feed"
msgstr "ब्लॉग फीड"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:774
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this field to record the &URL; associated with this contact's web log, "
"or blog."
msgstr "&URL; अस्य सम्पर्कस्य जालवृत्तेन, अथवा ब्लोग् इत्यनेन सह सम्बद्धम् ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:778
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show messages ..."
msgstr "सन्देशान् दर्शयतु ..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:778
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this Drop Down Box to override the corresponding message display option "
"in &kmail;'s <guibutton>&nbsp;Privacy &amp; Security&nbsp;</guibutton> "
"configuration menu. Choose <quote>Default</quote> to leave it up to &kmail;. "
"Choose <quote>Plain Text</quote> or <quote>HTML</quote> if you want to "
"override &kmail;'s default behavior when you receive a message from this "
"person."
msgstr ""
"&kmail; इत्यस्य <guibutton>&nbsp;गोपनीयता &amp; सुरक्षा&nbsp;</guibutton> "
"विन्यासमेनू। &kmail;पर्यन्तं त्यक्तुं <quote>पूर्वनिर्धारितं</quote> चिनोतु । यदि भवान् "
"अस्मात् व्यक्तितः सन्देशं प्राप्नोति तदा &kmail; इत्यस्य पूर्वनिर्धारितव्यवहारं अधिलिखितुं "
"इच्छति चेत् <quote>सादा पाठ</quote> अथवा <quote>HTML</quote> इति चिनोतु ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:784
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allow remote content ..."
msgstr "दूरस्थसामग्रीम् अनुमन्यताम् ..."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:784
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option if you want to override the corresponding message display "
"option in &kmail;'s <guibutton>&nbsp;Privacy &amp; Security&nbsp;</"
"guibutton> configuration menu when you receive a message from this person."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् &kmail; इत्यस्य <guibutton>&nbsp;गोपनीयता &amp; सुरक्षा&nbsp;</"
"guibutton> विन्यासमेनू यदा भवान् अस्मात् व्यक्तितः सन्देशं प्राप्नोति।"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:789
#, no-c-format
msgid "&nbsp;✔&nbsp;OK&nbsp;"
msgstr "&nbsp;✔&nbsp;ठीकम्&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:789
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to save the changes you have made. This button performs "
"the same function in all seven tabs appearing in the "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Add Contact&nbsp;&nbsp;"
"</guibutton> dialog."
msgstr ""
"भवता कृतानि परिवर्तनानि रक्षितुं एतत् विकल्पं चिनोतु । इदं बटनं "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>संपर्कं योजयतु&nbsp इत्यत्र "
"दृश्यमानेषु सप्तसु ट्याब्षु समानं कार्यं करोति ;&nbsp;</guibutton>संवादः ।"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:794
#, no-c-format
msgid "&nbsp;⦸&nbsp;Cancel&nbsp;"
msgstr "&nbsp;⦸&nbsp;रद्द करो&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:794
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to leave the "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>Add Contact&nbsp;&nbsp;"
"</guibutton> dialog without saving your changes. This button performs the "
"same function in all seven tabs appearing in the <quote>Add Contact</quote> "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"list-add.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>सम्पर्कं योजयतु&nbsp;&nbsp;"
"</guibutton> त्यक्तुं एतत् विकल्पं चिनोतु संवादं भवतः परिवर्तनं न रक्षितम्। एतत् बटन् "
"<quote>संपर्कं योजयतु</quote> संवादे दृश्यमानेषु सप्तसु ट्याब्षु समानं कार्यं करोति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:806
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Location Tab"
msgstr "स्थानं ट्याब्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:808
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the data input fields in the <quote>Location</quote> tab shown below to "
"associate one or more snail-mail addresses with this person."
msgstr ""
"अस्मिन् व्यक्तिना सह एकं वा अधिकं वा घोंघा-मेल-सङ्केतं सम्बद्धं कर्तुं अधः दर्शिते <quote>स्थान</"
"quote> ट्याब् मध्ये दत्तांशनिवेशक्षेत्राणां उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:813
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Location</quote> tab.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>स्थान</quote> ट्याब् ।</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:819
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Location</quote> tab.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>स्थान</quote> ट्याब्।</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:822
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Location</quote> tab, part of the <quote>Add "
"Contact</quote> dialog."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>स्थान</quote> ट्याब्, <quote>सम्पर्कं योजयतु</quote> "
"संवादस्य भागः ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:832
#, no-c-format
msgid "(unlabeled) Drop Down Box"
msgstr "(अलेबल) Drop Down Box"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:832
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this list of categories to describe each mailing address for this "
"contact. Available options include &nbsp;<quote>Home</quote>, <quote>Work</"
"quote>, <quote>Postal</quote>, &etc;"
msgstr ""
"अस्य सम्पर्कस्य प्रत्येकं मेलपतेः वर्णनार्थं श्रेणीनां एतस्याः सूचीयाः उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु । "
"उपलब्धविकल्पेषु &nbsp;<quote>गृहं</quote>, <quote>कार्यं</quote>, <quote>डाक</"
"quote>, इत्यादयः सन्ति;"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:837
#, no-c-format
msgid "Street / Post Office Box / Postal Code / Locality / Region"
msgstr "गली / डाकघर पेटी / डाक कोड / स्थानीयता / क्षेत्र"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:837
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use these free-form data fields to enter mailing address data: Street "
"Address, PO Box, ZIP Code, City, and State, respectively, for addresses in "
"the U.S.A."
msgstr ""
"मेल-पतेः-दत्तांशं प्रविष्टुं एतेषां मुक्त-रूप-दत्तांशक्षेत्राणां उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु: क्रमशः स्ट्रीट्-पतेः, "
"PO Box, ZIP Code, City, State च, U.S.A."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:842
#, no-c-format
msgid "Country"
msgstr "देशः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:842
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this Drop Down Box to select a country, from Afghanistan to Zimbabwe."
msgstr ""
"अफगानिस्तानतः जिम्बाब्वेपर्यन्तं देशस्य चयनार्थं एतस्य Drop Down Box इत्यस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:846
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is the preferred address"
msgstr "एतत् प्राधान्यं सम्बोधनम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:846
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check this box to designate the preferred, or default, mailing address."
msgstr "प्राधान्यं, अथवा पूर्वनिर्धारितं, मेल-सङ्केतं निर्दिष्टुं एतत् पेटीं चिनोतु ।"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: index.docbook:850
#, no-c-format
msgid "&nbsp;Add Address&nbsp;"
msgstr "&nbsp;पतेः योजयतु&nbsp;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:850
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you have finished entering address data, left click this button to add "
"a new address to the set of saved addresses appearing in the large display "
"window to the right."
msgstr ""
"यदा भवान् पतादत्तांशं प्रविष्टुं समाप्तवान् तदा दक्षिणतः विशाले प्रदर्शनविण्डो मध्ये दृश्यमानस्य "
"रक्षितसङ्केतसमूहे नूतनं पता योजयितुं एतत् बटन् वामनुदतु ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:855
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Icon<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-edit.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> in the large display "
"window"
msgstr ""
"बृहत् प्रदर्शनविण्डो मध्ये चिह्नं<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"document-edit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:857
#, no-c-format
msgid "Left click this icon to edit the associated address data."
msgstr "सम्बद्धं पतादत्तांशं सम्पादयितुं एतत् चिह्नं वामक्लिक् कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:860
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Icon<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-delete.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> in the large display "
"window"
msgstr ""
"बृहत् प्रदर्शनविण्डो मध्ये चिह्नं<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"edit-delete.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:862
#, no-c-format
msgid "Left click this icon to delete the associated address data."
msgstr "तत्सम्बद्धं पतादत्तांशं विलोपयितुं एतत् चिह्नं वामक्लिक् कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:870
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Business, Personal, and Notes Tabs"
msgstr "व्यापारः, व्यक्तिगतः, टिप्पणीः च ट्याब्स्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:872
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The next three tabs in the <quote>Add Contact</quote> dialog are even "
"simpler than the <quote>Location</quote> tab. They allow you to save some "
"information about this person's business and professional affiliations, a "
"few personal details, and miscellaneous free-form notes, respectively."
msgstr ""
"<quote>संपर्कं योजयतु</quote> संवादे अग्रिमत्रय ट्याब् <quote>स्थान</quote> ट्याब् "
"इत्यस्मात् अपि सरलतरम् अस्ति । ते भवन्तं क्रमशः अस्य व्यक्तिस्य व्यापारस्य "
"व्यावसायिकसम्बद्धतायाः च विषये काश्चन सूचनाः, कतिपयानि व्यक्तिगतविवरणानि, विविधानि "
"मुक्त-रूप-टिप्पण्यानि च रक्षितुं शक्नुवन्ति"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:879
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Business</quote> tab.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>व्यापार</quote> ट्याब् ।</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:885
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Business</quote> tab.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>व्यापार</quote> ट्याब्।</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:888
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Business</quote> tab, part of the <quote>Add "
"Contact</quote> dialog."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>व्यापार</quote> ट्याब्, <quote>सम्पर्कं योजयतु</quote> "
"संवादस्य भागः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:897
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Business</quote> tab, shown above, lets you save some additional "
"details about this person's professional and business associations. All the "
"input fields are free-form; you may enter any kind of text data in each "
"field. The small <guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"document-open.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject></guibutton> button will open a file search dialog, making "
"it easy to associate a filename with this person's <quote>Free/Busy</quote> "
"schedule, if you wish."
msgstr ""
"उपरि दर्शितं <quote>व्यापार</quote> ट्याब् अस्य व्यक्तिस्य व्यावसायिकव्यापारसङ्घस्य विषये "
"केचन अतिरिक्तविवरणानि रक्षितुं शक्नोति । सर्वे निवेशक्षेत्राणि मुक्तरूपाः सन्ति; प्रत्येकस्मिन् "
"क्षेत्रे भवान् किमपि प्रकारस्य पाठदत्तांशं प्रविष्टुं शक्नोति । लघु "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-"
"open.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton> "
"बटनं सञ्चिका अन्वेषणसंवादं उद्घाटयिष्यति, कृत्वा अस्य व्यक्तिस्य <quote>Free/Busy</quote> "
"समयसूचना सह सञ्चिकानाम सम्बद्धं कर्तुं सुलभम्, यदि भवान् इच्छति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:904
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Notice that you should enter your business associate's phone as a telephone "
"number under the <quote><link linkend=\"edit-contact-tab\">Contact</link></"
"quote> tab. Similarly, his office address is entered via the "
"<quote>Location</quote> tab, as described in <link linkend=\"edit-location-"
"tab\">the preceding section</link>."
msgstr ""
"लक्ष्यतां यत् भवन्तः स्वस्य व्यापारिकसहकारिणः दूरभाषं दूरभाषसङ्ख्यारूपेण अन्तर्गतं "
"प्रविष्टव्याः<quote><link linkend=\"edit-contact-tab\"> संपर्कः</link></quote> टब "
"। तथैव तस्य कार्यालयस्य पता मार्गेण प्रविष्टः भवति<quote> स्थानीय</quote> टब इति यथा "
"वर्णितम्<link linkend=\"edit-location-tab\"> पूर्वखण्डः</link> ."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:911
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Personal</quote> tab.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>व्यक्तिगत</quote> ट्याब् ।</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:917
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Personal</quote> tab.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>व्यक्तिगत</quote> ट्याब्।</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:920
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Personal</quote> tab, part of the <quote>Add "
"Contact</quote> dialog."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>व्यक्तिगत</quote> ट्याब्, <quote>सम्पर्कं योजयतु</quote> "
"संवादस्य भागः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:929
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this tab to store a few personal details: this person's birthday, his "
"wedding anniversary, and the name of his partner, or significant other. "
"Click one of the buttons (&eg;, <guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"view-calendar-birthday.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton>&nbsp;) to enter his date of "
"birth, or his wedding anniversary."
msgstr ""
"कतिपयानि व्यक्तिगतविवरणानि संग्रहीतुं एतस्य ट्याब् इत्यस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु: अस्य व्यक्तिस्य "
"जन्मदिनम्, तस्य विवाहस्य वार्षिकोत्सवः, तस्य सहभागिनः नाम च, अथवा महत्त्वपूर्णः अन्यः। "
"बटन् मध्ये एकं नुदन्तु (&उदा., <guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"view-calendar-birthday.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton> &nbsp;) तस्य जन्मतिथिं, तस्य "
"विवाहवार्षिकी वा प्रविष्टुं ।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:938
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Notes</quote> tab.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>टिप्पणी</quote> ट्याब् ।</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:944
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Notes</quote> tab.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>टिप्पणी</quote> ट्याब् ।</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:947
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Notes</quote> tab, part of the <quote>Add Contact</"
"quote> dialog."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>टिप्पण्याः</quote> ट्याब्, <quote>सम्पर्कं योजयतु</"
"quote> संवादस्य भागः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:956
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <quote>Notes</quote> tab provides a totally free-form input area in "
"which you may enter any data you want to associate with this person."
msgstr ""
"<quote>टिप्पणयः</quote> ट्याब् सर्वथा मुक्तरूपं निवेशक्षेत्रं प्रदाति यस्मिन् भवान् अस्मिन् "
"व्यक्तिना सह सम्बद्धं कर्तुम् इच्छति यत्किमपि दत्तांशं प्रविष्टुं शक्नोति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:964
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Tricky Stuff"
msgstr "द ट्रिकी स्टफ"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:966
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook; provides a couple of more complex data storage features, in "
"addition to the simple functions described in the preceding section."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook; पूर्वभागे वर्णितस्य सरलकार्यस्य अतिरिक्तं द्वे द्वे "
"अधिकजटिलदत्तांशसञ्चयविशेषताः प्रदाति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:970
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Custom Fields Tab"
msgstr "कस्टम् फील्ड्स् ट्याब्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:972
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Not happy with the wide array of data items that &kaddressbook; has already "
"pre-programmed for you? Well, you're in luck. Someday -- maybe soon --you "
"may utilize the <quote>Custom Fields</quote> dialog shown below to define "
"and populate as many additional data fields as you can possibly use."
msgstr ""
"न प्रसन्नः दत्तांशवस्तूनाम् विस्तृतसरण्या यत् &kaddressbook; भवतः कृते पूर्वमेव पूर्वप्रोग्रामं "
"कृतवान् अस्ति? साधु, भवतः भाग्यम् अस्ति। कदाचित् -- सम्भवतः शीघ्रमेव --भवन्तः अधः "
"दर्शितस्य <quote>Custom Fields</quote> संवादस्य उपयोगं कृत्वा यावन्तः अतिरिक्ताः "
"दत्तांशक्षेत्राणि परिभाषितुं जनयितुं च शक्नुवन्ति ।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:978
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Custom Fields</quote> tab.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>अनुकूलक्षेत्राणि</quote> ट्याब् ।</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:984
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Custom Fields</quote> tab.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>अनुकूलक्षेत्राणि</quote> ट्याब् ।</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:987
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Custom Fields</quote> tab, part of the <quote>Add "
"Contact</quote> dialog."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>अनुकूलक्षेत्राणि</quote> ट्याब्, <quote>सम्पर्कं योजयतु</"
"quote> संवादस्य भागः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:996
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is an experimental feature which doesn't yet do anything worth talking "
"about. So I'm not going to say anything else about it."
msgstr ""
"एतत् प्रयोगात्मकं विशेषता अस्ति यत् अद्यापि किमपि वक्तुं योग्यं न करोति। अतः अहं तस्य विषये "
"अन्यत् किमपि न वक्ष्यामि।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1004
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Crypto Settings Tab"
msgstr "क्रिप्टो सेटिंग्स् ट्याब्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1006
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Need to send a confidential email message that ought not be read by prying "
"eyes? &kaddressbook; provides a simple way for you to associate "
"cryptographic keys with each person on your mailing list."
msgstr ""
"गोपनीयं ईमेलसन्देशं प्रेषयितुं आवश्यकता अस्ति यत् अन्वेषकैः नेत्रैः न पठितव्यम्? &kaddressbook; "
"भवतः मेलसूचिकायां प्रत्येकेन व्यक्तिना सह क्रिप्टोग्राफिक-कुंजी-सम्बद्धं कर्तुं सरलं मार्गं प्रदाति ।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1011
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Crypto Settings</quote> tab.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>क्रिप्ट् सेटिङ्ग्स्</quote> ट्याब् ।</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1017
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Crypto Settings</quote> tab.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>क्रिप्ट् सेटिंग्स्</quote> ट्याब् ।</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1020
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Crypto Settings</quote> tab, part of the <quote>Add "
"Contact</quote> dialog."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>क्रिप्ट् सेटिंग्स्</quote> ट्याब्, <quote>सम्पर्कं योजयतु</"
"quote> संवादस्य भागः ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1030
#, no-c-format
msgid "Allowed Protocols"
msgstr "अनुमत प्रोटोकॉल"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1030
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose which mode of encryption you wish to use when sending a message to "
"this person: <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-inline-pgp\">Inline OpenPGP</"
"glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-open-pgp\">OpenPGP/&MIME;</"
"glossterm>, <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-mime\"><acronym>S/MIME</acronym> </"
"glossterm>, or <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-opaque\"><acronym>S/MIME</acronym> "
"Opaque</glossterm>."
msgstr ""
"अस्य व्यक्तिं प्रति सन्देशं प्रेषयन्ते सति भवान् कस्य गोपनविधानस्य उपयोगं कर्तुम् इच्छति इति "
"चिनोतु: <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-inline-pgp\">Inline OpenPGP</glossterm>, "
"<glossterm linkend=\"gloss-open-pgp\">OpenPGP/ &MIME;</glossterm>, "
"<glossterm linkend=\"gloss-mime\"><acronym>S/MIME</acronym> </glossterm>, "
"अथवा <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-opaque\"><acronym>S/MIME</acronym> अपारदर्शक</"
"glossterm> ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1036
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preferred OpenPGP Encryption Key:"
msgstr "प्राधान्यं OpenPGP एन्क्रिप्शन कुञ्जी:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1036
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guibutton>&nbsp;Change...&nbsp;</guibutton> button to select from a "
"list of available Open<glossterm linkend=\"gloss-pgp\">PGP</glossterm> keys, "
"if you have chosen OpenPGP encryption. Use the "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-clear."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject></guibutton> button "
"to clear a previously selected key."
msgstr ""
"उपलब्धानां Open<glossterm linkend=\"gloss-pgp\">PGP</glossterm> कीलानां सूचीतः "
"चयनार्थं <guibutton>&nbsp;परिवर्तनं...&nbsp;</guibutton> बटनस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु, यदि "
"भवान् OpenPGP एन्क्रिप्शनं चिनोति पूर्वं चयनितं कीलं स्वच्छं कर्तुं "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-clear."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject></guibutton> बटनस्य "
"उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1042
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preferred <acronym>S/MIME</acronym> Encryption Certificate:"
msgstr "प्राधान्यं <acronym>S/MIME</acronym> एन्क्रिप्शन प्रमाणपत्रम्:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1043
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guibutton>&nbsp;Change...&nbsp;</guibutton> button to select from a "
"list of available certificates, if you are using a verified key. Use the "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-clear."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton> button "
"to clear a previously selected key."
msgstr ""
"उपलब्धप्रमाणपत्रसूचिकातः चयनार्थं <guibutton>&nbsp;परिवर्तनं...&nbsp;</guibutton> "
"बटनस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु, यदि भवान् सत्यापितं कुञ्जीम् उपयुङ्क्ते । पूर्वं चयनितं कीलं स्वच्छं कर्तुं "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-clear."
"png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton> बटनस्य "
"उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1048
#, no-c-format
msgid "Message Preference / Sign:"
msgstr "सन्देशप्राथमिकता / चिह्नम् :"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1048
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this drop-down box to specify when messages addressed to this person "
"should bear your cryptographic signature: Never / Always / If Possible / Ask."
msgstr ""
"अस्य व्यक्तिस्य सम्बोधितसन्देशेषु कदा भवतः क्रिप्टोग्राफिकहस्ताक्षरं भवितुमर्हति इति निर्दिष्टुं "
"एतस्य ड्रॉप्-डाउन-पेटिकायाः उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु: कदापि / सर्वदा / यदि सम्भवं / पृच्छन्तु ।"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:1052
#, no-c-format
msgid "Message Preference / Encrypt:"
msgstr "सन्देशप्राथमिकता / एन्क्रिप्ट् :"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1052
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use this drop-down box to specify when messages addressed to this person "
"should be encrypted by using the selected protocol and key: Never / Always / "
"If Possible / Ask."
msgstr ""
"चयनितप्रोटोकॉलस्य कीलस्य च उपयोगेन अस्य व्यक्तिस्य सम्बोधितसन्देशाः कदा एन्क्रिप्टेड् भवेयुः "
"इति निर्दिष्टुं एतस्य ड्रॉप्-डाउन-पेटिकायाः उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु: कदापि / सर्वदा / यदि सम्भवं / "
"पृच्छन्तु ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1065
#, no-c-format
msgid "Command Reference"
msgstr "आदेश सन्दर्भ"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1068
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Menu Bar"
msgstr "मेनू पट्टिका इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1070
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here is a rundown of the seven menus appearing on &kaddressbook;'s Menubar."
msgstr "अत्र &kaddressbook;'s Menubar इत्यत्र दृश्यमानानां सप्तमेनूणां रनडाउन् अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1074
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "सञ्चिकामेनू इति"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1078
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>File</quote> menu.</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>सञ्चिका</quote> मेन्यू इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् ।</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1084
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>File</quote> menu.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>सञ्चिका</quote> मेन्यू इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् ।</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1087
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>File</quote> menu after clicking the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu></menuchoice> button on the Menubar."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>File</quote> मेन्यू मेन्यूबार इत्यत्र "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu></menuchoice> इति बटन् नुत्वा ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1096
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu></menuchoice> menu lets you access "
"six main functions, three of which have several options."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu></menuchoice> मेन्यू भवन्तं षट् मुख्यकार्यं प्राप्तुं "
"शक्नोति, येषु त्रयेषु अनेकाः विकल्पाः सन्ति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>New&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"list-add.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>New "
"Contact</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu> <guisubmenu>नवीन&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"सूची-जोड.png\"। format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>नव सम्पर्क</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This has exactly the same effect as clicking the <guibutton>&nbsp; &plus;"
"&nbsp;New Contact&nbsp;</guibutton> button on the Toolbar. See <link linkend="
"\"how-to-add-a-new-contact\">chapter 2 above</link> for complete details."
msgstr ""
"एतस्य प्रभावः यथा क्लिक् करणेन भवति तथा एव भवति<guibutton> + नव सम्पर्क</guibutton> "
"Toolbar इत्यत्र बटनं कुर्वन्तु । पश्यतु<link linkend=\"how-to-add-a-new-contact\"> "
"उपरि २ अध्यायः</link> सम्पूर्णविवरणार्थम्।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>New&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"user-group-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>New "
"Group</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>G</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu> <guisubmenu>नवीन&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu> <guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"उपयोक्तृ-समूह-नव.png\"। format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>नवसमूह</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a dialog in which you may define a new group, or mailing list. See "
"&nbsp;<link linkend=\"file-new-group\">the appendix</link> for a detailed "
"explanation of this function."
msgstr ""
"एकं संवादं उद्घाटयति यस्मिन् भवान् नूतनं समूहं, अथवा मेलसूचीं परिभाषितुं शक्नोति । पश्यतु<link "
"linkend=\"file-new-group\"> परिशिष्टम्</link> अस्य कार्यस्य विस्तृतव्याख्यानार्थम् ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>New&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"folder-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Add "
"Address Book</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu><guisubmenu>नवीन&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"folder-new.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></ imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>पतापुस्तकं योजयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This opens the <quote>Add Address Book</quote> dialog, which is fully "
"documented in &nbsp;<link linkend=\"how-to-add-a-new-address-book\">chapter "
"2 above</link>."
msgstr ""
"एतेन उद्घाट्यते<quote> पतापुस्तकं योजयतु</quote> संवादः, यः पूर्णतया दस्तावेजितः "
"अस्ति<link linkend=\"how-to-add-a-new-address-book\"> उपरि २ अध्यायः</link> ."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Import&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Import from LDAP server ...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu><guisubmenu>आयात&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>LDAP सर्वरतः आयातं ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This function allows you to import data from an <acronym>LDAP</acronym> "
"server. The server must be configured before you can use this function. See "
"<link linkend=\"configure-ldap-server\">the appendix</link> for full details."
msgstr ""
"एतत् कार्यं भवन्तं <acronym>LDAP</acronym> सर्वरात् दत्तांशं आयातयितुं शक्नोति । भवन्तः "
"एतत् कार्यं उपयोक्तुं शक्नुवन्ति तस्मात् पूर्वं सर्वरं विन्यस्तं भवितुमर्हति । पश्यतु<link linkend="
"\"configure-ldap-server\"> परिशिष्टम्</link> पूर्णविवरणार्थम्।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1132
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Import&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Import CSV file ...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu><guisubmenu>आयात&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>CSV सञ्चिकां आयातयतु ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This function allows you to import contact data from a comma separated "
"values (<acronym>csv</acronym>) file. A dialog ensues, in which you may "
"associate each field in the input file with a named field in "
"&kaddressbook;'s internal storage record. See <link linkend=\"import-csv-data"
"\">the appendix</link> for a more detailed explanation."
msgstr ""
"एतत् कार्यं भवन्तं अल्पविरामेन पृथक्कृतमूल्यानां ( <acronym>csv</acronym> ) सञ्चिकातः "
"सम्पर्कदत्तांशं आयातयितुं शक्नोति । संवादः भवति, यस्मिन् भवान् निवेशसञ्चिकायां प्रत्येकं क्षेत्रं "
"&amp;kaddressbook;इत्यस्य आन्तरिकभण्डारणअभिलेखे नामकृतेन क्षेत्रेण सह सम्बद्धं कर्तुं शक्नोति । "
"पश्यतु<link linkend=\"import-csv-data\"> परिशिष्टम्</link> अधिकविस्तृतव्याख्यानार्थम् ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Import&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Import vCard ...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu><guisubmenu>आयात&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>विकार्ड आयातयतु ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This function facilitates the importation of <acronym>vcf</acronym>, or "
"vCard, data. All three versions of vCard are supported. You can learn more "
"about the vCard formats <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/VCard"
"\">at this web site</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"एतत् कार्यं <acronym>vcf</acronym>, अथवा vCard, दत्तांशस्य आयातं सुलभं करोति । vCard "
"इत्यस्य त्रयः अपि संस्करणाः समर्थिताः सन्ति । vCard प्रारूपाणां विषये अधिकं ज्ञातुं शक्नुवन्ति "
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/VCard\">अस्मिन् जालपुटे</ulink> ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Export&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Export CSV file ...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu><guisubmenu>निर्यात&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>CSV सञ्चिका निर्यातयतु ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This function allows you to export selected contact data as a Comma "
"Separated Values (<acronym>csv</acronym>) file. There are 47 fields in the "
"output record. Please refer to <link linkend=\"export-csv-data\">the "
"appendix</link> for a list of those data fields."
msgstr ""
"एतत् कार्यं भवन्तं चयनितं सम्पर्कदत्तांशं Comma Separated Values ( <acronym>csv</"
"acronym> ) सञ्चिकारूपेण निर्यातयितुं शक्नोति । आउटपुट् अभिलेखे ४७ क्षेत्राणि सन्ति । कृपया "
"देखें<link linkend=\"export-csv-data\"> परिशिष्टम्</link> तेषां दत्तांशक्षेत्राणां सूचीयाः "
"कृते ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Export&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Export vCard 4.0 ...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu><guisubmenu>निर्यात&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>vCard 4.0 निर्यातं कुर्वन्तु ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1152
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This function allows you to export selected contact data as a file in "
"<acronym>vCard 4.0</acronym> format. See <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/VCard\">this Wikipedia article</ulink> for more information."
msgstr ""
"एतत् कार्यं भवन्तं <acronym>vCard 4.0</acronym> प्रारूपेण चयनितसम्पर्कदत्तांशं सञ्चिकारूपेण "
"निर्यातयितुं शक्नोति । अधिकविवरणार्थं <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"VCard\">अयं विकिपीडियालेखः</ulink> पश्यन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Export&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Export vCard 3.0 ...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu><guisubmenu>निर्यात&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>vCard 3.0 निर्यातं कुर्वन्तु ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1158
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This function allows you to export selected contact data as a file in "
"<acronym>vCard 3.0</acronym> format. This format is similar to "
"<acronym>vCard 4.0</acronym> format."
msgstr ""
"एतत् कार्यं भवन्तं <acronym>vCard 3.0</acronym> प्रारूपेण चयनितसम्पर्कदत्तांशं सञ्चिकारूपेण "
"निर्यातयितुं शक्नोति । एतत् प्रारूपं <acronym>vCard 4.0</acronym> प्रारूपस्य सदृशम् अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Export&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Export vCard 2.1 ...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu><guisubmenu>निर्यात&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>vCard 2.1 निर्यातं कुर्वन्तु ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This function allows you to export selected contact data as a file in "
"<acronym>vCard 2.1</acronym> format. This format is similar to "
"<acronym>vCard 3.0</acronym> format."
msgstr ""
"एतत् कार्यं भवन्तं <acronym>vCard 2.1</acronym> प्रारूपेण चयनितसम्पर्कदत्तांशं सञ्चिकारूपेण "
"निर्यातयितुं शक्नोति । एतत् प्रारूपं <acronym>vCard 3.0</acronym> प्रारूपस्य सदृशम् अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-"
"print.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>Print</"
"guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>P</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref= \"document-"
"print.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>मुद्रण</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1172
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a printer selection dialog. Use the "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"document-preview-archive.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Print Preview</guisubmenu></menuchoice> dialog below to "
"set up the range of names and the print format before you select this "
"function."
msgstr ""
"मुद्रकचयनसंवादं उद्घाटयति । "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"document-preview-archive.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>मुद्रणपूर्वावलोकन</guisubmenu></ इत्यस्य उपयोगं कुर्वन्तु । "
"menuchoice> संवादं अधः कृत्वा नामपरिधिं मुद्रणस्वरूपं च सेट् कर्तुं पूर्वं भवता एतत् कार्यं "
"चिन्वन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"document-preview-archive.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Print Preview</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सञ्चिका</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"document-preview-archive.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>मुद्रणपूर्वावलोकन</guisubmenu >"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a print preview dialog, which also permits you to format the report, "
"select which items to include, and specify a sort order, &etc; See &nbsp;"
"<link linkend=\"file-print-preview\">the appendix</link> for further details."
msgstr ""
"मुद्रणपूर्वावलोकनसंवादं उद्घाटयति, यत् भवन्तं प्रतिवेदनं स्वरूपयितुं, केषां वस्तूनि समाविष्टुं "
"चिन्वन्तु, क्रमाङ्कनं च निर्दिशति, &amp;etc; पश्यतु<link linkend=\"file-print-preview"
"\"> परिशिष्टम्</link> अधिकविवरणार्थम्।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Q</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"application-"
"exit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>Quit</"
"guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>प्रश्न</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>सञ्चिका</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref= "
"\"application-exit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </"
"inlinemediaobject>निर्गम</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1188
#, no-c-format
msgid "Closes the &kaddressbook; application."
msgstr "&kaddressbook; अनुप्रयोगः।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1198
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Edit Menu"
msgstr "सम्पादन मेनू इति"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1202
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Edit</quote> menu.</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>Edit</quote> मेन्यू इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् ।</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Edit</quote> menu.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>Edit</quote> मेन्यू इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् ।</"
"phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Edit</quote> menu after clicking the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu></menuchoice> button on the Menubar."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>Edit</quote> मेन्यू मेन्यूबार इत्यत्र "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu></menuchoice> इति बटन् नुत्वा ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1220
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu></menuchoice> menu lets you access "
"eight main functions, two of which have multiple options."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu></menuchoice> मेन्यू भवन्तं अष्टौ मुख्यकार्यं प्राप्तुं "
"शक्नोति, येषु द्वयोः बहुविकल्पाः सन्ति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1226
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"document-edit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Edit "
"Contact ...</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सम्पादन</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"document-edit.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>सम्पर्क सम्पादयतु ...</ guisubmenu> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1228
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This has nearly the same effect as clicking the <guibutton>&nbsp;&plus;&nbsp;"
"New Contact&nbsp;</guibutton> button on the Toolbar. The difference is that "
"this menu item allows you to edit a contact record that already exists, "
"instead of creating a brand new one. See <link linkend=\"how-to-add-a-new-"
"contact\">chapter 2 above</link> for complete details."
msgstr ""
"एतस्य प्रभावः प्रायः तथैव भवति यथा क्लिक् करणेन<guibutton> + नव सम्पर्क</guibutton> "
"Toolbar इत्यत्र बटनं कुर्वन्तु । अन्तरं तु एतत् यत् एतत् मेनू-वस्तु भवन्तं पूर्वमेव विद्यमानं सम्पर्क-"
"अभिलेखं सम्पादयितुं शक्नोति, न तु नूतनं निर्मातुं । पश्यतु<link linkend=\"how-to-add-a-new-"
"contact\"> उपरि २ अध्यायः</link> सम्पूर्णविवरणार्थम्।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-cut.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Cut Contact ...</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>सम्पादन</guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref= \"edit-cut.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject>संपर्कं कटयतु ...</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Performs a <quote>Cut</quote> operation on the selected contact. A copy of "
"this contact, in <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-vcf\"><acronym>vCard 3.0</"
"acronym></glossterm> format, is placed on the clipboard. The <quote>Cut</"
"quote> will be completed when you <quote>Paste</quote> this contact "
"somewhere."
msgstr ""
"चयनितसम्पर्कस्य उपरि <quote>Cut</quote> कार्यं करोति । अस्य सम्पर्कस्य प्रतिलिपिः, "
"<glossterm linkend=\"gloss-vcf\"><acronym>vCard 3.0</acronym></glossterm> "
"प्रारूपेण, क्लिप्बोर्ड् मध्ये स्थापिता अस्ति । यदा भवान् एतत् सम्पर्कं कुत्रचित् <quote>Paste</"
"quote> करोति तदा <quote>Cut</quote> पूर्णं भविष्यति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"edit-copy.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Copy "
"Contact ...</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सम्पादनं</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"edit-copy.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>संपर्कस्य "
"प्रतिलिपिः ...</ guisubmenu> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Places a copy of this contact on the clipboard, so you can paste it "
"somewhere else."
msgstr ""
"अस्य सम्पर्कस्य प्रतिलिपिं क्लिप्बोर्ड् मध्ये स्थापयति, अतः भवान् अन्यत्र चिनोतुम् अर्हति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1248
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-paste.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Paste</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>V</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>सम्पादन</guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref= \"edit-paste.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject>चिपकतु</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1250
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<quote>Pastes</quote> the cut or copied contact at the current location. "
"This may be in the same address book you did the <quote>Cut</quote> or "
"<quote>Copy</quote> from, or in another address book. Since the preceding "
"operations placed the contact information on the system's clipboard, you may "
"also paste it somewhere else besides &kaddressbook; (&eg; into a text "
"editor, or as a <acronym>vCard 3.0</acronym> file in your home folder)."
msgstr ""
"<quote>कट् अथवा प्रतिलिपिकृतं सम्पर्कं वर्तमानस्थाने चिनोति</quote> । एतत् भवता "
"<quote>Cut</quote> अथवा <quote>Copy</quote> इति तस्मिन् एव पतापुस्तके, अन्यस्मिन् वा "
"सम्बोधनपुस्तके वा भवितुम् अर्हति । यतः पूर्वक्रियाभिः सम्पर्कसूचना प्रणाल्याः क्लिप्बोर्ड् मध्ये "
"स्थापिता, भवान् &kaddressbook; (&eg; पाठसम्पादके, अथवा भवतः गृहपुटे <acronym>vCard "
"3.0</acronym> सञ्चिकारूपेण) ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"edit-copy.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>Copy "
"Contact To &nbsp; &gt;</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>(a variable list)</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सम्पादनं</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"edit-copy.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>सम्पर्कं "
"प्रतिलिख्य &nbsp; &gt;</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>(एकं चरसूची)</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Combines the <quote>Copy</quote> and <quote>Paste</quote> operations into a "
"single click of the &LMB;. The list of destinations displayed depends on how "
"many address books you have created."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Copy</quote> तथा <quote>Paste</quote> क्रियाः &LMB; इत्यस्य एकस्मिन् क्लिक् "
"मध्ये संयोजयति । प्रदर्शितानां गन्तव्यस्थानानां सूची भवता कति पतापुस्तकानि निर्मिताः इति "
"निर्भरं भवति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-"
"jump.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>Move Contact "
"To &nbsp; &gt;</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>(a variable list)</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सम्पादनं</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-"
"jump.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>सम्पर्कं &nbsp; "
"&gt;</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>(एकं चरसूची)</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Works just like the <quote>Copy Contact To</quote> operation described "
"above, except that it combines <quote>Cut</quote> and <quote>Paste</quote> "
"into a single click of the &LMB;."
msgstr ""
"उपरि वर्णितस्य <quote>Copy Contact To</quote> क्रियायाः इव कार्यं करोति, केवलं "
"<quote>Cut</quote> तथा <quote>Paste</quote> इत्येतत् &LMB; इत्यस्य एकस्मिन् क्लिक् "
"मध्ये संयोजयति इति व्यतिरिक्तम् ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"press\">&Del;</keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> "
"<imagedata fileref=\"edit-delete.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Delete Contact</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"press\">&Del;</keycombo></"
"shortcut><guimenu>सम्पादन</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref="
"\"edit-delete.png\" प्रारूपम् =\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>संपर्कं "
"विलोपयन्तु</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1273
#, no-c-format
msgid "Delete the selected contact from the current address book."
msgstr "वर्तमान पतापुस्तकात् चयनितं सम्पर्कं विलोपयन्तु।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1277
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"edit-delete.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Delete "
"Address Book</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सम्पादन</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"edit-delete.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>पतापुस्तकं विलोपयतु</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1279
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Delete the current address book. Be careful with this command -- you could "
"lose some data! In theory, this function simply removes the symbolic link "
"between &kaddressbook; and the associated <acronym>vCard</acronym> file or "
"directory (or the hyperlink to a <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-cloud\">cloud-"
"based service</glossterm>), and the real data will not be altered. Still, "
"it's probably wisest to make a backup copy of this address book somewhere "
"before you delete it."
msgstr ""
"वर्तमान पतापुस्तकं विलोपयन्तु। एतेन आदेशेन सावधानाः भवन्तु -- भवान् किञ्चित् दत्तांशं नष्टुं "
"शक्नोति! सिद्धान्ततः एतत् कार्यं केवलं &kaddressbook; तथा च सम्बद्धं <acronym>vCard</"
"acronym> सञ्चिका अथवा निर्देशिका (अथवा <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-cloud\">मेघ-"
"आधारितसेवा</glossterm> इत्यस्य अतिलिङ्क्), तथा च वास्तविकदत्तांशः परिवर्तितः न "
"भविष्यति तथापि, सम्भवतः अस्य पतापुस्तकस्य विलोपनात् पूर्वं कुत्रचित् बैकअपप्रतिं करणीयम् ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:1292
#, no-c-format
msgid "The View Menu"
msgstr "दृश्य मेनू इति"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>View</quote> menu.</"
"screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>दृश्य</quote> मेन्यू इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् ।</"
"screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>View</quote> menu.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>दृश्य</quote> मेन्यू इत्यस्य स्क्रीनशॉट् ।</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1305
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>View</quote> menu after clicking the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu></menuchoice> button on the Menubar."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook; इत्यस्य <quote>दृश्य</quote> मेन्यू मेन्यूबार इत्यत्र "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu></menuchoice> इति बटन् नुत्वा ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1314
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu></menuchoice> menu lets you access "
"four main functions, and one experimental feature which doesn't really do "
"anything yet."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu></menuchoice> मेन्यू भवन्तं चत्वारि मुख्यकार्यं, "
"अपि च एकं प्रयोगात्मकं विशेषतां प्राप्तुं शक्नोति यत् वास्तवतः अद्यापि किमपि न करोति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1321
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Themes &nbsp; &gt;</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>दृश्य</guimenu><guisubmenu>विषयाणि &nbsp; &gt;</guisubmenu> इति"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu item doesn't really do anything. It will open a <quote>Themes</"
"quote> dialog, but that dialog is broken in release 5.10.3."
msgstr ""
